    Browser -->|"HTTP Request"| MW
    MW --> Login & Users & Depts & Roles & Leave & Holidays

    Login --> LoginSvc
    Users --> UserSvc
    Depts --> DeptSvc
    Roles --> JobRoleSvc
    Leave --> LeaveSvc
    Holidays --> HolidaySvc

    LoginSvc & UserSvc & DeptSvc & JobRoleSvc & LeaveSvc & HolidaySvc --> ORM

    ORM <-->|"SQL queries"| UsersTable
    ORM <-->|"SQL queries"| LeaveTable
    ORM <-->|"SQL queries"| DeptTable
    ORM <-->|"SQL queries"| JobRoleTable
    ORM <-->|"SQL queries"| HolidayTable

    ORM -->|"JSON Response"| Browser
